headline: CBRE (CBRE): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: CBRE has been on fire lately. In the past six months alone, the company’s stock price has rocketed 57%, reaching $139.81 per share. This was partly thanks to its solid quarterly results, and the performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
